NAME

Memoize::Lift - lift expression evaluation to compile time

DESCRIPTION

This module supplies an operator that causes an expression to be evaluated
immediately at compile time, memoising its value for use at runtime.

INSTALLATION

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

